<div class="big_container">

  <nav class="navbar nav-home navbar-fixed-top fixed-top" id="theNavbar">

    <!-- logo redirection homepage -->
    <%= link_to "/", class: "navbar-brand d-flex" do %>
      <div class="d-flex">
        <div class="logoCoworkspace">
        <%= image_tag "logo_coworkspace.svg" %>
        </div>
        <h2 class="name-site my-0 pl-2">COWORKSPACE</h2>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <form class="form-inline">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "Find a space", spaces_path, class: "btn  btn-home-signin btn-outline-light mx-2" %>
          <button class=" nav-item dropdown btn mx-2" type="button">
              <%= cl_image_tag current_user.avatar, class: "avatar dropdown-toggle", id: "navbarDropdown", data: { toggle: "dropdown" }, 'aria-haspopup': true, 'aria-expanded': false %>

            <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown">
              <%= link_to "Profile", user_path(:id), class: "dropdown-item" %>
              <%= link_to "Log out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "dropdown-item" %>
            </div>
          </button>
      <% elsif owner_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "Manage your space", owner_dashboard_path(:id), class: "btn  btn-home-signin btn-outline-light mx-2" %>
        <%= link_to "Log out", destroy_owner_session_path, method: :delete%>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Coworking", new_owner_session_path, class: "btn-nav-link nav-item mx-5" %>
        <%= link_to "Entreprise", new_owner_session_path, class: "btn-nav-link nav-item mx-5" %>

        <button class=" nav-item btn-nav-link-sign-in btn ml-5 mr-4" type="button">
          <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: "nav-link" %>
        </button>
      <% end %>
    </form>
  </nav>


  <div class="header d-flex">
    <div class="home_ellipse">
      <%= image_tag "ellipse_home.svg" %>
    </div>
    <div class="slogan_title">
      <h1 class="home_slogan">Find your desk all over the world ! </h1>
      <h3 class="home_title pt-2">From private offices to open spaces <br>
          we will find a space that suits you perfectly.
      </h3>

      <div class="">
              <%= form_tag spaces_path, method: :get, class:"form-inline mt-5" do %>
        <%= text_field_tag :query,
          params[:query],
          class: "form-control form-control-home",
          placeholder: "Select a city" %>
          <%= date_field_tag :arrival_date, params[:arrival_date], class: "form-control-home form-control", placeholder: "12/11/2020" %>
          <%= submit_tag 'Find', class:"btn-custom btn-home-search mx-2" %>
      <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home_illusta ">
      <div class="home_sun"></div>
      <%= image_tag "home_illustration.svg"%>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="home_about background-grey text-center py-5" >
      <div data-aos="zoom-in">
          <h3 class=" title_home ">About us</h3>
          <p class="text_about">Less alone than at home and more professional than in a coffee shop, Cowork Space has been installed all over the world since 2019. A place of work, exchange and sharing of skills for all entrepreneurs, self-employed, freelancers, project leaders and teleworkers wishing to break the isolation of their homes and develop a quality professional network.</p>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="explication_home d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center my-4" id="explication_step_1">
    <div class="description_content_home" data-aos="fade-right">
      <h3 class="title_home">All Around The World</h3>
      <p class="text_description">Located all over the world, you can find your Coworking Space <strong>everywhere</strong> ! <br>
      We offers you clean and modern spaces, adapted to your needs. Because your <strong>success</strong> is our priority. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="illustation_home" data-aos="fade-left">
      <%= image_tag "planete.svg"%>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="explication_home d-flex justify-content-center my-5 py-5 align-items-center background-grey py-4" id="explication_step_2" data-aos-delay="1000" data-aos-anchor="#explication_step_1" >
    <div class="illustation_home" data-aos="fade-right">
      <%= image_tag "clock.svg"%>
    </div>
    <div class="description_content_home" data-aos="fade-left">
      <h3 class="title_home">Save Timer</h3>
      <p class="text_description">Optimize your working time by finding a place where can book and play <strong>immediately</strong>. CoworkSpace avoid to wait too much time to receive a host answer.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="explication_home d-flex justify-content-center  my-4 align-items-center" id="business" data-aos-delay="2000" data-aos-anchor="#explication_step_2" >
    <div class="description_content_home" data-aos="fade-right" >
      <h3 class="title_home">Business Environment</h3>
      <p class="text_description">You will have the opportunity to meet professionals from the same sector of activity, exchanges between members will allow you to enrich each other, to <strong>create synergies</strong> , working groups, skills associations, etc. Group spirit contributes to strengthening <strong>motivation and productivity.</strong>  </p>
    </div>
    <div class="illustation_home" data-aos="fade-left">
      <%= image_tag "team.svg"%>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center background-blue my-4 py-5">
    <h3 class="title_home mb-5">Customers Reviews</h3>
    <div class=" d-flex avis_customer mb-3" >
      <div class="avis_customer_box mx-4 py-4" data-aos="zoom-out" id="trigger-left">
        <p class=" text_avis text-left  pl-5">With others tools we found ourselves constantly waiting on responses to questions, the payment process and the validation is very fast. </p>
        <div class="client_info d-flex ml-4 align-items-center ">
          <%= image_tag "avatar_girl.svg"%>
          <div class="text-left pl-3 ">
            <h5>Ana Longo</h5>
            <p>Director of Clients Relations </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="avis_customer_box mx-4 py-4" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-delay="500"
     data-aos-anchor="#trigger-left" >
        <p class=" text_avis text-left  pl-5">We are a remote team working across multiple timeszones. Coworkspace is a great tool where I can book easily my coworking ! I can find what Iwe looking for immediately, and leave a comment for others to view if itâ€™s convenient for them.  </p>
        <div class="client_info d-flex ml-4 align-items-center"  >
          <%= image_tag "avatar_man.svg"%>
          <div class="text-left align-items-center pl-3">
            <h5>Simon Hebert</h5>
            <p>Product Owner Freelance, Paris </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="deroulement" style="padding: 110px 80px;">
    <h2 class="mb-5" id="step-trigger-1" data-aos="fade-right"
     >Getting started has <br>never been easier</h2>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">

      <div class=" mx-4 d-flex" id="step-trigger-2" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="500"
     data-aos-anchor="#step-trigger-1">
        <h3 class="number-circle">1</h3>
        <div class="deroulement-content">
          <h3 class="">Choose your <br>coworkplace</h3>
          <p>There is more 3490 coworking in more than 25 country. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class=" mx-4 d-flex" id="step-trigger-3" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="800"
     data-aos-anchor="#step-trigger-2">
        <h3 class="number-circle">2</h3>
        <div class="deroulement-content">
          <h3 class="">Set the date <br>of your stay</h3>
          <p>Plan your stay with or without your team. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="  mx-4 d-flex" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="1100"
     data-aos-anchor="#step-trigger-3">
        <h3 class="number-circle">3</h3>
        <div class="deroulement-content">
          <h3 class="">Easy Paiment <br> Process</h3>
          <p>Just pay and receive the confirmation. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>

    <button class="btn-nav-link-sign-in justify-content-center d-flex" style="margin: 70px auto;width: 200px" type="button">
          <%= link_to "Try Now !", new_user_session_path, class: "nav-link " %>
    </button>
</div>
